{"tid":431714,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"派咩散水餅好","createTime":"2017-10-11T02:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T05:02:41.000Z","uid":2034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"393b76e77fd659a40e269eb5499c8a9b1ffec54c","tid":431714,"uid":2034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"早排食咗東海堂，難食到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下月走，一請就要請全公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，起碼30人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時諗到以下兩間<br />\n<br />\n1) 西樹泡芙<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chouxcreme.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chouxcreme.com.hk%2F&d=%2FK3SEECyrwcl5LYrHhxdoP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b198fea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chouxcreme.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n有泡芙同忌廉窩夫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/104641_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F104641_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=95323925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/104641_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F104641_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=73576422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同東海堂差唔多價，呢間好食又多口味選擇<br />\n<br />\n2) Luna Cake<br />\n<a href=\"http://lunacake.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flunacake.com%2F&d=%2FK3SEECyrwcl5LYrHhxdoP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0536449c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lunacake.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n有cheesecake同大福個類<br />\n不過偏貴，貪佢完整一個蛋糕夠好睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/105120_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F105120_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png&h=9ce3b71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/105121_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F105121_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png&h=6ef66c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩間都有得送貨，求巴絲俾下啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者建議其他都可以"},{"pid":"fa76507fe13df5d97a0aa6349ab6d88a003f9864","tid":431714,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"標準答案: cova"},{"pid":"7a485b02921ecf8e394d0c6a3ac79656a3e5088c","tid":431714,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"咩budget？<br />\n做咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"15b05aa8be4bb4a03dc678a72231e129a85e1278","tid":431714,"uid":10330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"咁有錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73affbf3527d99adb2a745b6a99feb324016726","tid":431714,"uid":2034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩budget？<br />\n做咗幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$500-600左右<br />\n做咗一年，同事上司老闆都待我不薄"},{"pid":"702781cf1c2a34e5b884c99f338d03274297159c","tid":431714,"uid":2034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案: cova</blockquote><br />\n窮撚買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c90cfabd1f91a007fd29d645dabfbea89b4f96e","tid":431714,"uid":51387,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-Q4TWypztwChqZEkUPz139XJYFeV_TW4DpMlJbrWJaz0MuZqnjpB7fFCyAyg6YP0TS9fv8i2VPNCEaESeDMAo7vvyrwUc_Q=s0